Package org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.governanceaction.search

Class MapTypePropertyValue

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.governanceaction.search.PropertyValue
org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.governanceaction.search.MapTypePropertyValue
public class MapTypePropertyValue extends PropertyValue
MapTypePropertyValue stores the values of a map within an entity, struct or relationship properties. The elements of the map are stored in an ElementProperties map.
